301
00:19:41,600 --> 00:19:44,300
- Having fun yet?
- I'm starting to miss the Mississippi.

302
00:19:44,500 --> 00:19:47,900
- The mud, floods?
- Mike, you have a call on your private line.

303
00:19:48,100 --> 00:19:51,200
