00:28:32,000 --> 00:28:33,300
Rachel!

431
00:28:33,500 --> 00:28:35,000
Give me your hand!

432
00:28:36,800 --> 00:28:39,100
- Oh, God. Come on!
- Help!

433
00:28:41,300 --> 00:28:44,100
- Someone help me!
- I'm burning up!

434
00:28:44,300 --> 00:28:47,400
I'm burning up! My legs are burning!

435
00:28:47,700 --> 00:28:49,100
Hold on, Rachel!

436
00:29:14,800 --> 00:29:16,800
Oh, b...

