461
00:30:43,000 --> 00:30:45,100
I want you to get all helicopters up now.

462
00:30:45,100 --> 00:30:48,200
Bob, we need pictures.
I need those choppers in the air now.

463
00:30:48,500 --> 00:30:51,700
