464
00:30:51,900 --> 00:30:55,600
Poles are all up, but there's no light.
A lotta haze here.

465
00:30:55,800 --> 00:30:57,600
Let me in there, Brian.

466
00:30:57,600 --> 00:31:01,900
Yeah, looks like
power's down everywhere in the city.

467
00:31:02,200 --> 00:31:03,600
