468
00:31:03,800 --> 00:31:06,200
Get in? Come on, Boss,
you know I sleep on your desk.

469
00:31:06,400 --> 00:31:07,800
Disaster is my life.

470
00:31:10,400 --> 00:31:12,400
He's kidding, right?

471
00:31:12,500 --> 00:31:18,000
It's too early to hear from
the California lnstitute of Geological Studies...

472
00:31:21,700 --> 00:31:22,800
Dad!

473
00:31:25,100 --> 00:31:26,600
Hold it. Wh-what was that?

474
00:31:28,600 --> 00:31:30,600
